channel.title: Need team for devlopment of HellzEnd
channel.description:
Hello,
Im looking to start my all new Client, Server, logo's etc. I need a good team that can help out in this task. All of you will be put into credits and other parts of this. Out work will be well known once it starts rolling. This will be somthing unlike any other. we will use places in the server that have not been used. And places coded to look new and refreshed. to be part of this team just Message me or reply to this.
Currenly needed spots
Coder Logo designer Clinter Designer
Thank you, HellzEnd Support and Helldemon
